inks ==\n\n{{sisterlinks|s=Author:Rudolph William Louis Giuliani|d=Q212648|c=Category:Rudy Giuliani|b=no|v=no|voy=no|m=no|mw=no|wikt=no|species=no|n=Category:Rudy Giuliani}}\n* {{CongLinks | congbio= | votesmart= | fec=P00003251 | congress= }}<!-- \nLinks formerly displayed via the CongLinks template:\n* [http://www.opensecrets.org/politicians/summary.php?cid=N00009908 Financial information (federal office)] at [[Center for Responsive Politics|OpenSecrets.org]]\n* [http://www.ontheissues.org/Rudy_Giuliani.htm Issue positions and quotes] at [[On the Issues]]\n* [http://www.worldcat.org/identities/lccn-nr95-32260 Works by or about Rudy Giuliani] in libraries ([[WorldCat]] catalog)\n* [http://www.c-spanvideo.org/rudolphgiuliani Appearances] on [[C-SPAN]] programs\n* [http://www.charlierose.com/guest/view/1480 Appearances] on [[Charlie Rose (TV show)|''Charlie Rose'']]\n* [https://www.theguardian.com/world/rudygiuliani Collected news and commentary] at ''[[The Guardian]]''\n* [http://topics.nytimes.com/top/reference/timestopics/people/g/rudolph_w_giuliani/index.html Collected news and commentary] at ''[[The New York Times]]''\n* -->\n* {{C-SPAN|rudolphgiuliani}}\n* {{curlie|Regional/North_America/United_States/Government/Elections/President/2008/Candidates/Giuliani,_Rudy}}\n* [http://www.laguardiawagnerarchive.lagcc.cuny.edu/COLLECTIONS.aspx?ViwType=1&ColID=9 La Guardia and Wagner Archives/The Giuliani Collection]\n*TPM infographic: [https://talkingpointsmemo.com/muckraker/rudy-giuliani-foreign-clients-map Tracking Rudy Giuliani's Foreign Dealings]\n\n{{s-start}}\n{{s-legal}}\n{{s-bef|before=John Shenefield}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[United States Associate Attorney General]]|years=1981\u20131983}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[D. Lowell Jensen|Lowell Jensen]]}}\n|-\n{{s-bef|before=[[John S. Martin Jr.|John Martin]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[United States Attorney for the Southern District of New York]]|years=1983\u20131989}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Benito Romano]]<br />{{small|Acting}}}}\n|-\n{{s-ppo}}\