 April 1989\n| Anniversaries\n| Four\n|\n|-\n| 16 May 1989\n|[[Europe|Europa]], Toys and games\n| Four\n|\n|-\n| 4 July 1989\n| Industrial [[Archaeology]]\n| Four\n|\n|-\n| 25 July 1989\n| Industrial Archaeology (Miniature Sheet)\n| One (MS)\n|\n|-\n| 5 September 1989\n| 150th Anniversary of [[Royal Microscopical Society]]\n| Four\n|\n|-\n| 17 October 1989\n| [[Lord Mayor's Show]], [[London]]\n| Five\n|\n|-\n| 14 November 1989\n| Christmas\n| Five\n| [[David Gentleman]]<ref name=\"gentleman103stamps\"/>\n|-\n|}\n\n== Acknowledgements ==\n* [[Stanley Gibbons]]\n* [[Concise Stamp Catalogue]]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20110609001644/http://www.gibbonsstampmonthly.com/ Gibbons Stamp Monthly]\n* Royal Mail Stamp Guide\n* Royal Mail British Philatelic Bulletin\n\n==Other Decades==\n* [[List of United Kingdom commemorative stamps|Great Britain commemorative stamps 1924\u201369]]\n* [[Great Britain commemorative stamps 1970\u201379]]\n* [[Great Britain commemorative stamps 1990\u201399]]\n* [[Great Britain commemorative stamps 2000\u201309]]\n* [[Great Britain commemorative stamps 2010\u201319]]\n* [[Great Britain commemorative stamps 2020\u201329]]\n\n==See also==\n{{Portal|Philately}}\n* [[Stanley Gibbons]]\n* [[Stamp Collecting]]\n* [[List of people on stamps]]\n* [[Philately]]\n* [[Postage stamp|Stamps]]\n* [[PHQ Cards]]\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20070203143655/http://www.stanleygibbons.com/home/index.asp Stanley Gibbons Stamps Shop Homepage]\n* [http://www.royalmail.com Royal Mail]\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Great Britain commemorative stamps 1980-1989}}\n[[Category:Postage stamps of the United Kingdom|1980]]\n[[Category:1980s in the United Kingdom|Commemorative stamps]]\n[[Category:Lists of postage stamps]]\n[[Category:United Kingdom philately-related lists|Commemorative]]\n[[Category:Commemorative stamps]]\n", "name_user": "Gumby61", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eHistory:Add artist/designer", "url_pa